<div class="row collapse" id="add-activity">
  <% if @message %>
    <div class="message-bottle">
      <p style="color:red; font-weight:bold; background:#ffb3b3; border:2px solid red; padding:1em;"><%= @message %></p>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  <h2>Code Checker</h2>
  <p>Welcome to the Maenporth Estate Offer Code Checker.  This form will check the authenticity of the offer code you have been presented with.  The form will tell you whether or not the offer code is valid and has genuinely been generated by the Maenporth Estate website.</p>
  <p>If the code is genuine, we will record the transaction value.  If the code is not genuine, nothing will be recorded in our database.</p>
  <p>If you have any questions please contact Jessica Hodges:  jessica.hodges@maenporthestate.co.uk</p>
  <p style="font-style: italic;">Please note - you do not need to use a currency symbol.  Please just enter the value of the transaction to two decimal places: e.g. 250.50</p>
  <div class="large-6 columns end" id="codes-check">
    <form class="" action="/leisure/redeem-offer" method="post">
      <input type="text" placeholder="Offer code" required name="offer_code">
      <input type="number" placeholder="Transaction value: e.g. 125.50" required name="transaction_value" step='0.01'>
      <input type="submit" value="Check Code">
    </form>
  </div>
</div>
